snippet.title: Jeep Fire & Wrongful Death Case: Deposition of a Witness
snippet.description:
Jeb Butler from Butler Law Firm deposed a witness of a Jeep fire and wrongful death.

We’d love to hear what you think! It helps our clients if people watch these depositions and leave comments, because that helps us to know what jurors will take away from the depositions, and what questions jurors will have after watching them. So please feel free to comment with your thoughts (good or bad) and let us know what other questions you wish we’d asked. That’s the main reason we post these depositions to YouTube.

For more information about Jeep Fire & Wrongful Death Cases, see https://butlerfirm.com/jeep-fires-explosions/
